msgid "Koffi"
msgstr "Koffi"

#: ../../index.rst:5
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "总览"

#: ../../index.rst:7
msgid "Koffi is a **fast and easy-to-use C FFI module for Node.js**, featuring:"
msgstr "Koffi是一个**快速且易用的, Node.js下的C FFI模块**, 特点:"

#: ../../index.rst:9
msgid "Low-overhead and fast performance (see :ref:`benchmarks<Benchmarks>`)"
msgstr "低开销且高性能(参见 :ref:`基准测试<Benchmarks>`)"

#: ../../index.rst:10
msgid ""
"Support for primitive and aggregate data types (structs and fixed-size "
"arrays), both by reference (pointer) and by value"
msgstr ""
"支持原始类型和聚合类型(结构体和定长数组), 通过引用(指针)或值"

#: ../../index.rst:11
msgid "Javascript functions can be used as C callbacks (since 1.2.0)"
msgstr "Javascript函数可以用作C的回调(1.2.0引入)"

#: ../../index.rst:12
msgid ""
"Well-tested code base for :ref:`popular OS/architecture "
"combinations<Supported platforms>`"
msgstr ""
"对:ref:`常见的系统-架构组合<Supported platforms>`经过充分测试的代码库"

#: ../../index.rst:14
msgid ""
"Koffi requires a recent `Node.js <https://nodejs.org/>`_ version with "
"N-API version 8 support, see :ref:`this page<Node.js>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Koffi需要较新版本的[Node.js](https://nodejs.org/)，支持[N-API](https://nodejs.org/api/n-api.html)版本8, "
"参见:ref:`这里<Node.js>`获取更多信息."

#: ../../index.rst:16
msgid ""
"The source code is available here: https://github.com/Koromix/rygel/ (in "
"the *src/koffi* subdirectory)."
msgstr ""
"源代码可以在此获取: https://github.com/Koromix/rygel/ (*src/koffi*子目录中)"

#: ../../index.rst:18
msgid ""
"New releases are frequent, look at the :ref:`changelog<changelog>` for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"版本更新频繁, 查看:ref:`更新日志<changelog>`获取更多信息."

